## GWAS Systemic Lupus Erythematosus

This is an R Markdown document to obtain Manhattan Plot associating Systemic Lupus Erythematosus with variations in genome reported in the GWAS Catalogue.


**Falta cambiar datos

```{r }
library(gapminder)
data(gapminder)
d <- gapminder[which(gapminder$year == 2007), ]
knitr::kable(summary(d),
  caption = "Summary of the gapminder data in 2007"
)
```
